title: Team Nine is Now Recruiting
body:
Team Nine is hosting open tryouts for a jungler and a support for the start of the new season, be at least silver or higher and have a decent understanding of the game and somewhat of a large champ pool Leave a post if your interested and i will contact you in game. We currently use Curse Voice.
